          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Description of Service -->
        <div>
          <h2>Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            HeatherAI is an AI-powered nutrition coaching platform built on the coaching
            methodology of Heather Bauer, RD. The Service provides:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI-generated nutrition coaching and meal planning</li>
            <li>Photo-based meal logging and nutritional analysis</li>
            <li>Health and wellness data tracking</li>
            <li>Personalized coaching insights and recommendations</li>
            <li>Weekly coaching video summaries</li>
            <li>Access to registered dietitian sessions (AI + Human Coach plan)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Medical Disclaimer -->
        <div>
          <h2>Medical Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>HeatherAI is not a medical device, healthcare provider, or substitute for
            professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            HeatherAI is not currently FDA-registered or approved as a medical device. The coaching,
            meal plans, and recommendations provided are for informational and educational purposes
            only. They are based on general nutrition principles and Heather Bauer's coaching
            methodology, adapted by artificial intelligence to your stated preferences and goals.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            You should:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Always consult with a qualified healthcare professional before making changes to your diet, especially if you have medical conditions, take medications, or are pregnant or nursing</li>
            <li>Not rely on HeatherAI for medical diagnosis or treatment of any condition</li>
            <li>Seek immediate medical attention for any health emergencies</li>
            <li>Inform your healthcare provider about any dietary changes you make based on HeatherAI's guidance</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            If you are using GLP-1 medications (such as Ozempic, Wegovy, Mounjaro, or Zepbound),
            HeatherAI can provide nutritional coaching support, but medication management should
            always be directed by your prescribing physician.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Accounts -->
        <div>
          <h2>Accounts & Registration</h2>
          <p>
            To use HeatherAI's coaching features, you must create an account. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your login credentials</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized access to your account</li>
