          <h3>Available Plans</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Meal Logging (Free):</strong> AI meal logging, macro estimates, weight/water/caffeine tracking, and meal history at no cost</li>
            <li><strong>AI Coaching ($39/month):</strong> Full HeatherAI coaching, personalized meal plans, restaurant guidance, health trends, proactive check-ins, and personalized video coaching</li>
            <li><strong>AI + Human Coach ($299/month):</strong> Everything in AI Coaching plus 2 private Zoom sessions per month with a registered dietitian, personalized plan reviews, and priority support</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="mt-6">Billing</h3>
          <p>
            Paid subscriptions are billed monthly on the anniversary of your signup date.
            All fees are in U.S. dollars. You authorize us to charge your selected payment
