          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6">Cancellation</h3>
          <p>
            You may cancel your subscription at any time. Cancellation takes effect at the end
            of your current billing period. You will retain access to paid features until the
            end of the period you have already paid for. No refunds are provided for partial
            billing periods.
