          <h3 class="mt-6">Price Changes</h3>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to change subscription prices. We will provide at least 30 days'
            notice of price changes. Continued use of the Service after a price change constitutes
            acceptance of the new pricing.
          </p>
        </div>

